{"tid":2331671,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個新發明足以顛倒整個世界的戰爭模式","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T01:29:36.000Z","uid":38539,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4bea6c0200ba748d32723fc868683431d8060b0f","tid":2331671,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無聽過釹磁鐵？<br />\n簡單啲講釹磁鐵是現今磁性最強的永久磁鐵，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJfgeFa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJfgeFa.gif&h=d8537394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種磁鐵是由日本發明家佐川真人於1982首次發現，<br />\n在下圖，佐川真人就示範釹磁鐵磁力的強勁，<br />\n重量1公克的釹磁鐵可以舉起1900公克重水瓶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2FoD6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2FoD6O.png&h=ffbdcc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為釹磁鐵擁有極強的磁力，<br />\n所以廣泛應用係電子產品，例如手機、耳機等等，<br />\n甚至係美國最先進的醫院已經引入釹磁石儀器做外科手術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vV1CJyF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvV1CJyF.gif&h=7de209c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中醫生們正在為在戰場上被手榴彈碎片插入身體的傷者施展手術，<br />\n利用釹磁石儀器用超強磁力將殘留在身體碎片更安全拿出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imMZWTJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimMZWTJ.gif&h=afce9f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而係上個月美國最新發明咗一種微型釹磁鐵，<br />\n令釹磁鐵可以更加廣泛應用係不同的領域，<br />\n<br />\n我嘅諗法係咁的，<br />\n地球上大部份武器，包括熱、冷武器主要成份都係由金屬製造而成，<br />\n如果我哋發明一種盾牌利用微型釹磁鐵做塗層，<br />\n每當有人用槍械射你，只要你打開個釹磁鐵盾牌，<br />\n任何子彈都會飛向塊盾牌，而唔會有人中彈傷亡，<br />\n人類將會回復原始人用石頭木棒扑人的時代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zoca3yQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoca3yQ.gif&h=680d6310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「動畫將現實融入故事，而我將虛幻變為實物。」<br />\n「如果諾貝爾話能夠操控火藥者，就等於操縱未來；我就話能夠操控磁力者，就等於返回過去。」<br />\n我有預感五十年後，呢兩句名言和我個大名將會出現係各國的教科書裡面。"},{"pid":"234b85095309a4ecf7a1ffe659a9d17c70def5a0","tid":2331671,"uid":368978,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"1. 金屬=/=有磁性<br />\n2. let distance be d, magnetic force f1 = f0/d^2<br />\n<br />\n結論：唔work"},{"pid":"efce5560d68c2882b0dfac45a85bb6b9ec466d5b","tid":2331671,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb7baf1f74d1e9a51b5448486179c862c5a348a3","tid":2331671,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a26bb883d50bfe477faaf59e4f6134e57fb4c3a","tid":2331671,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"原來你就係萬磁王 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ecd09bfc7bd85c30467f39ae86ed8bacf083d7","tid":2331671,"uid":387761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e1a55e452fcd8d659c3e0703a0bc0edff05711e","tid":2331671,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"銅吸唔到"},{"pid":"b91f2c3046359fed5d64525ffbaf7d23f5723b56","tid":2331671,"uid":245998,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係gif仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e94f9ac4870caf5cc6e6577f2ff993d8ecdf8c","tid":2331671,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"圖中醫生們正在為在戰場上被手榴彈碎片插入身體的傷者施展手術<br />\n<br />\nironman嚟個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a9c5c0d757f40a35f55a4edd3ead4b0a7aa802","tid":2331671,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img